      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "$4,500 - Older vehicle in poor overall condition and priced accordingly. This is best suited for someone looking for a project, repair candidate, or possible parts car rather than a clean daily driver. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, age-related deterioration, and likely mechanical needs before regular use. If you want something inexpensive to tinker with and you understand what a rough older vehicle entails, this may be worth a look.",
