    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean, well-kept vehicle in mint condition. The exterior presents beautifully with a glossy finish and no meaningful cosmetic issues to note, and the interior is equally impressive with very little visible wear. It has clearly been cared for, feels tight and fresh throughout, and should make an excellent choice for a buyer looking for a top-condition example.",
