      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, practical, and priced to move, this vehicle is a great fit for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values function and value over cosmetics, but it still offers a lot of usefulness at an accessible price point. If you're looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overspending, this is a compelling option.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without all the fluff? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for a first car, a backup vehicle, or someone who just needs simple, dependable transportation at a price that makes sense. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind a little cosmetic wear, this could be a really smart buy.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong enthusiast appeal. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels fundamentally workable, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable car they can sort and enjoy. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but the bones are there, and with some attention this one can make a rewarding daily, weekend toy, or tuner-style build. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Runs, drives, gets the job done. Cosmetically rough, priced to move fast. Great beater, work car, or project.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of road-worn charm that turns an ordinary drive into a story. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014instead, it offers honest character, a bold presence, and the kind of project-ready potential that speaks to someone who sees opportunity where others see age. Whether you need an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on weekend revival, or a platform with personality, this one brings plenty of spirit and a chance to make it your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a smart choice for a buyer looking for affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It offers dependable everyday utility, straightforward ownership, and excellent value for someone who appreciates a lower entry price with room to make it their own. A practical option for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels without overpaying.",
      "price": 6795.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    }
